== 家庭 ==
迪瓦茨和妻子生有两个儿子，Luka和Matija以及一个收养的女儿<ref>[http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0228615/bio Vlade Divac Internet Movie Database Inc. biography] {{Wayback|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0228615/bio |date=20090605074532 }}, retrieved April 29, 2007</ref> 他的養女的双亲在[[科索沃战争|科索沃战争]]时被科索沃解放军所射杀<ref>[http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/inside_game/magazine/lifeofreilly/1999/0524/ Vlade Divac's Private War] {{Wayback|url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/inside_game/magazine/lifeofreilly/1999/0524/ |date=20070808183836 }}, by Rick Reilly, CNN/SI, published May 25, 1999, retrieved April 29, 2007</ref>

